    &lt;button @click&#x3D;&quot;decrement&quot;&gt;-&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;
    &lt;button @click&#x3D;&quot;incrementOdd&quot;&gt;当前求和为奇数再加&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;
